version_description: - Bug fixes and improvements.
Apple Pay is here! Now it’s even easier to pay for your transfer. Once you have your credit or debit card added to your Apple wallet, it’s just a few clicks to pay.
- Bug fixes and improvements.

Need to contact customer service? We’ve made it easier for you to get help. Tap on ‘Contact us’ on the help screen, select the area you need help with and send us a message.
